{"tid":1899950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗政府遭指隱匿新冠肺炎疫情 , 反控美國散布恐懼!","createTime":"2020-02-27T02:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T04:15:15.000Z","uid":318316,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f57b485e28ee4ddc723d16a3411ce5900e112fb1","tid":1899950,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"伊朗總統羅哈尼（Hassan Rouhani）今天指控美國，在致命的新型冠狀肺炎(COVID-19，俗稱武漢肺炎)疫情爆發之際藉機散布恐懼，他還反譏美國才疲於應對新冠肺炎，境內甚至有1萬6000人死於流行性感冒。<br />\n<br />\n目前伊朗國內有139起2019年冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）確診病例，其中19人喪命，連伊朗衛生部副部長哈利奇（Iraj Harirchi）也染病，疫情的致死人數在全球僅次於中國。<br />\n<br />\n在美國國務卿（Mike Pompeo）指控伊朗當局隱匿疫情訊息後，隔天羅哈尼在每週例行的內閣會議表示：「我們不應該讓美國在冠狀病毒這件事上加諸一種新病毒，這種病毒被稱為&hellip;極度恐懼。」<br />\n<br />\n羅哈尼指出，美國人「自己才疲於應對冠狀病毒，美國有1萬6000人死於流感，但他們卻避而不談。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6807623/article-%E9%81%AD%E6%8C%87%E9%9A%B1%E5%8C%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%8F%8D%E6%8E%A7%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6807623%2Farticle-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259A%25B1%25E5%258C%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2595%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2587%25BC%2F&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=c271d1cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6807623/article-%E9%81%AD%E6%8C%87%E9%9A%B1%E5%8C%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%8F%8D%E6%8E%A7%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC/</a>"},{"pid":"f964dea776f653a9e606de6d3427125c2ff3aa7d","tid":1899950,"uid":997,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"睇你個賤種咀口硬得幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"